---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden relative group">
        <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-64 h-64 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-700"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-primary-content mb-4 tracking-tight">
                    ¿Listo para exportar tus productos?
                </h2>
                <p class="text-primary-content/80 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Conoce toda la documentación y normativas internacionales necesarias para llevar tu mercancía al siguiente nivel sin contratiempos.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <a href="/requisitos" class="btn btn-lg bg-white border-none text-primary hover:bg-base-200 shadow-xl gap-3 px-8 text-lg font-bold">
                <Icon name="lucide:file-text" class="w-6 h-6" />
                VER REQUISITOS
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer class="bg-base-300 text-base-content pt-16 pb-8 mt-auto">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">
            
            <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-1">
                <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 group">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform shadow-lg">
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:shopping-bag"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-content"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter gradient-text">
                        ECO-EXPORTACIONES
                    </span>
                </a>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Líderes en logística internacional y distribución de productos eco-amigables. Conectando mercados globales con responsabilidad ambiental.
                </p>
                
                <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm text-base-content/80">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                        <Icon name="lucide:map-pin" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0" />
                        <span>Col. Kennedy Calle Principal</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon name="lucide:mail" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0" />
                        <span>contacto@eco-exportaciones.com</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Icon name="lucide:phone" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0" />
                        <span>+504 9766 5442</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <a href="https://wa.me/50497665442" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-circle btn-sm btn-ghost hover:bg-primary/20 hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="WhatsApp">
                        <Icon name="lucide:message-circle" class="w-5 h-5" />
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-circle btn-sm btn-ghost hover:bg-primary/20 hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="Twitter">
                        <Icon name="lucide:twitter" class="w-5 h-5" />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/exportspm/" class="btn btn-circle btn-sm btn-ghost hover:bg-primary/20 hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="Instagram">
                        <Icon name="lucide:instagram" class="w-5 h-5" />
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-circle btn-sm btn-ghost hover:bg-primary/20 hover:text-primary transition-colors" aria-label="Github">
                        <Icon name="lucide:github" class="w-5 h-5" />
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-span-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 text-base-content/90 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <Icon name="lucide:clock" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
                    Horario de Atención
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-base-content/70">
                    <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-base-content/10 pb-2">
                        <span>Lunes - Viernes:</span>
                        <span class="font-medium text-base-content text-right">8:00 AM - 6:00 PM</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-base-content/10 pb-2">
                        <span>Sábados:</span>
                        <span class="font-medium text-base-content text-right">9:00 AM - 2:00 PM</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex justify-between">
                        <span>Domingos:</span>
                        <span class="text-error font-medium text-right">Cerrado</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 text-base-content/90">
                    Servicios
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm">
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="text-base-content/60 hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-1 transition-all inline-block">Carga Marítima y Aérea</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="text-base-content/60 hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-1 transition-all inline-block">Gestión de Aduanas</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="text-base-content/60 hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-1 transition-all inline-block">Seguros de Mercancía</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#" class="text-base-content/60 hover:text-primary hover:translate-x-1 transition-all inline-block">Rastreo en Tiempo Real</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 text-base-content/90">
                    Suscríbete
                </h3>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Recibe reportes mensuales sobre las tendencias del mercado global de exportación.
                </p>
                <div class="form-control w-full">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <input
                            type="email"
                            placeholder="correo@empresa.com"
                            class="input input-bordered w-full pr-12 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary text-sm"
                        />
                        <button
                            class="absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-l-none btn btn-primary px-3"
                            aria-label="Subscribe"
                        >
                            <Icon name="lucide:arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5" />
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-base-content/10 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-base-content/50">
            <p>
                &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} ECO-EXPORTACIONES S.A. Todos los derechos reservados.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-6">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-base-content transition-colors">Aviso Legal</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-base-content transition-colors">Política de Cookies</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-base-content transition-colors">Términos de Servicio</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .gradient-text {
        background: linear-gradient(
            135deg,
            oklch(var(--p)) 0%,
            oklch(var(--s)) 100%
        );
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }
</style>